name: BisphosphonateAllergyIntolerance
title: Bisphosphonate allergy intolerance
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Codes that if returned in FHIR Allergy Intolerance resource would indicate bisphosphonate allergy, adverse effect, or intolerance),(Data Element Scope: Codes of bisphosphonate allergy and adverse effect as well as codes for bisphosphonates as drugs or substances),(Inclusion Criteria: SNOMED CT and ICD-10-CM codes),(Exclusion Criteria: NA)
